{"tid":2416332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：接種疫苗早好過遲　可以達到群體免疫   令通關等有更好條件","createTime":"2021-02-21T03:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T09:54:17.000Z","uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d20abbe0219b5cedc28052fd316fcd9bc36d7abd","tid":2416332,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，當局對新冠病毒疫苗接種已準備就緒，未來一星期接受市民預約，星期五就開始接種。她說接種疫苗可保護自己，一定好過不接種，很多人對此持觀望態度，但早接種一定好過遲接種。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始在一個電台節目說，全球每日新增個案數字雖然大，但亦有回落，很多專家認為可能與開始接種疫苗有關。因此她呼籲市民接種，越多人接種對社會效益越大，越快可以達到群體免疫，對恢復正常生活及通關等都有更好條件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576630-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576630-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=52d7a031\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576630-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=455dba7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576630-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"aabdb19e0b72dfc73418c20b3de9f7394531918d","tid":2416332,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"陳肇始呼籲市民接種，越多人接種對社會效益越大，越快可以達到群體免疫，對恢復正常生活及通關等都有更好條件。"},{"pid":"f810edf8680b2fd7214f2d605f7c847cc8afa46c","tid":2416332,"uid":183758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aabdb19e0b72dfc73418c20b3de9f7394531918d","tid":2416332,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"陳肇始呼籲市民接種，越多人接種對社會效益越大，越快可以達到群體免疫，對恢復正常生活及通關等都有更好條件。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"陳姑娘你識碌鳩咩"},{"pid":"aaf54a1d216854bfee614d856ac741d78de73ad7","tid":2416332,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:11:18.000Z","msg":"中國生化致命疫苗殺