:15.000Z","msg":"陳肇始：「對個人自己，當然接種一定比不接種好。如果問何時接種較好、是否要再觀望，我也呼籲大家早打一定比遲打好。對整個社會而言，愈多人接種，一定對社會的效益愈大。」"},{"pid":"ae86bb140964f9b9beadd1ee030611538b0b8c6a","tid":2416332,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官以及全體司局長會在本周初率先接種疫苗，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始指，希望能在社會上起示範作用；又呼籲市民接種疫苗，讓社會盡早有群體免疫，為通關等提供有利條件。"},{"pid":"63773e734fe447d02bc4ab139bbe0500f2dc9da2","tid":2416332,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"50%點樣群體免疫<br />\n仲話公共衛生博士<br />\n陳笑恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f441080e150520ce6ac924ce41afdb82922f32","tid":2416332,"uid":239680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:42:56.000Z","msg":"冇人想通關喎而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bad9289b69639849973a2ef03396e63f0bc67b","tid":2416332,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:44:11.000Z","msg":"唔通關咪幾好，少咁多大陸西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04827c4581f482f97c25ab668970d4389ab5c11b","tid":2416332,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"打兩枝都係得6成<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ea7db7e75db5d3b47d72379e07be549580b0b5","tid":2416332,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"我想通關啵 想去日本既通關"},{"pid":"721bb821861aa52ff7694269f85f914912cf996b","tid":2416332,"uid":167394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"得6成 邊做到群體免疫"},{"pid":"127fed970fbe21e8f1f42a47b9571579c790d813","tid":2416332,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/fuck.gif\" 